A '''daisy grubber''' is a [[garden tool]] that is used to pull out [[root]]s.<ref>{{cite web|title=grubber|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=anecAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA776&dq=Daisy+Grubber&hl=en&sa=X&ei=o0yXUr2-B4fyqQGVo4GwDw&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=Daisy%20Grubber&f=false|work=Oxford Dictionary of English|publisher=[[Oxford University Press]]|accessdate=28 November 2013}}</ref>  It is effective because it can pull out deep roots yet cause little or no disturbance to the surrounding soil.

